// Somewhere in init code… Servo exampleServo = new Servo(1); // “1” is the PWM port where you have things plugged in, may need to be changed! exampleServo.setBounds(2.0, 1.5, 1.5, 1.5, 1.0);

// Somewhere in code that runs periodically… exampleServo.set(.5); // 0.0 - 1.0 to specify position for actuator
